&lt;/div>
&lt;p>This tells Copilot Chat to include the content of &lt;code>readme.prompt.md&lt;/code> as context for each request.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2>Example&lt;span class="hx-absolute -hx-mt-20" id="example">&lt;/span>
&lt;a href="#example" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section">&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>&lt;p>Suppose you want Copilot to always follow your projectâ€™s code style. Create &lt;code>.github/prompts/codestyle.prompt.md&lt;/code>:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="hextra-code-block hx-relative hx-mt-6 first:hx-mt-0 hx-group/code">
